item.title: CVE-2023-46677|2023-11-07T20:35:03.334Z -- projectworlds%20pvt.%20limited -- online%20job%20portal
item.description: Online Job Portal v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Unauthenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'txt_uname' parameter of the sign-up.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.

item.title: CVE-2023-46679|2023-11-07T20:38:42.878Z -- projectworlds%20pvt.%20limited -- online%20job%20portal
item.description: Online Job Portal v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Unauthenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'txt_uname_email' parameter of the index.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.
